00:27:15.186 --> 00:27:19.166
in BRCA1 mutation carriers are the

445
00:27:19.186 --> 00:27:22.006
basal type, but there is substantially a small but

446
00:27:23.206 --> 00:27:26.706
significant fraction that are luminal type and are hormone receptor

