485
00:29:24.906 --> 00:29:28.716
Genetic alterations in combination with gene expression changes and

486
00:29:29.126 --> 00:29:29.896
epigenetic changes,

487
00:29:31.006 --> 00:29:34.386
in my opinion, would be working together to drive the process.

488
00:29:35.526 --> 00:29:35.826
